definitions.definition: An imitation of laughter, often used to express scorn or disbelief. Often doubled or tripled ( haw haw or haw haw haw ).
examples: You think that song was good? Haw!

definitions.definition: An intermission or hesitation of speech, with a sound somewhat like "haw"; the sound so made.

definitions.definition: An instruction for a horse or other animal to turn towards the driver, typically left.
